responsible?

713
01:11:17,209 --> 01:11:19,882
- Stop it.
- You stop it.

714
01:11:20,049 --> 01:11:25,840
I've seen you use Mikey to push guys
away, and now you're doing it to me.

715
01:11:26,009 --> 01:11:30,082
- Get out!
- I live here!

716
