If I thought like that, we wouldn't
have had so much fun the first week.

725
01:12:17,529 --> 01:12:22,762
You're grossing me out.
Don't talk about sex and Daddy.

726
01:12:23,969 --> 01:12:27,279
Hi, Lupe.

727
