779
01:17:07,169 --> 01:17:11,447
- Is he taking a dump?
- No, he's thinking real hard.

780
01:17:14,489 --> 01:17:19,927
- I'll get you cleaned up.
- Use the washroom in the back.

781
01:17:20,089 --> 01:17:25,766
- He'll ask about his daddy.
- I want James to be the daddy.

782
01:17:25,929 --> 01:17:30,923
Don't do that here.
That's a $1 0,000 desk!

783
