792
01:18:26,529 --> 01:18:29,441
Ma loves you. Rona loves you.

793
01:18:29,609 --> 01:18:34,763
James loves you.
Mikey, do you love James?

794
01:18:37,249 --> 01:18:42,528
- Give him a call.
- Do you want to play telephone?

795
01:18:42,689 --> 01:18:45,442
Hello?

796
01:18:45,609 --> 01:18:50,558
It's for you. You take this one,
I'll take the other one.

797
01:18:50,729 --> 01:18:55,803
This is Lou Franklin,
I'm phoning about your grandfather.

798
01:18:55,969 --> 01:18:59,678
