The man can't speak English.

821
01:21:01,689 --> 01:21:05,318
- So can Grandpa stay?
- Of course.

822
01:21:05,489 --> 01:21:11,803
- Thank you.
- Thanks for coming down so fast.

823
01:21:14,009 --> 01:21:18,002
- Hi.
- Hi.

824
01:21:18,169 --> 01:21:23,801
- Your grandfather can stay.
- You didn't have to do that.

825
01:21:23,969 --> 01:21:28,918
- I wanted to do it.
- Let me give you a ride home.

826
01:21:29,089 --> 01:21:31,398
- Don't bother.
- Fine!

827
01:21:31,569 --> 01:21:35,960
D.J. , it's time for lunch.
Let's go.

828
01:21:36,129 --> 01:21:40,247
- Are you okay with him?
- Get the hell out of here.

829
01:21:42,249 --> 01:21:46,447
