843
01:22:56,129 --> 01:23:02,079
- That's lda's grandson.
- Come on, I'm in a hurry.

844
01:23:02,249 --> 01:23:07,767
- Here, fella, go find your grandma.
- Thanks for nothing.

845
01:23:07,929 --> 01:23:13,287
When the police get here,
will you show them these pictures?

846
01:23:13,449 --> 01:23:16,566
All right, I'm on the case now.

847
01:23:18,809 --> 01:23:22,518
That is exactly what I need.

848
01:23:22,689 --> 01:23:27,763
